    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s clean, dependable, and just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
