    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for precise torque delivery across the rev range. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its original kinematic excellence with fresh bushings and dampening. This vehicle represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, exhibiting minor aesthetic wear balanced by rigorous drivetrain upkeep and a recently performed valve shim adjustment. A quintessential analog machine for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
