    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, expected road wear of a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by a smoke-free cabin and an intuitive infotainment system that operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, a result of a consistent schedule of synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, mounted on original alloy wheels that are free of significant curb rash. This car has served as a reliable daily driver and is prepared for immediate use without any looming mechanical concerns. It comes complete with two sets of keys, the original owner's manual, and a full set of all-weather floor mats to protect your investment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
