    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It\u2019s in great shape, super reliable, and has been really well-loved over the years. The interior is nice and clean, and it drives like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun road trip! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make the next owner very happy. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
