    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8 engine. This example retains its mechanical purity with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Recent comprehensive service includes preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC-coated bearings and upgraded throttle actuators, addressing critical long-term reliability concerns. The chassis remains sharp, utilizing the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system to manage rebound and compression across varied surfaces. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering a linear power band up to the 8,400 RPM redline. The vehicle sits on forged Style 220M alloys wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, ensuring precise turn-in and high lateral acceleration.",
